    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Motion picture film with a 65-millimeter width, with sprocket-holes on both sides. Often transferred to 70mm projection film, for theatrical release.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
